{"tid":1033223,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界係咪得廣東歌歌詞要啱聲調？","createTime":"2019-02-23T03:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T17:42:19.000Z","uid":60288,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad574556dbef66341c69373094e612282827395","tid":1033223,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"廣東歌歌詞要啱聲調，唔啱會俾人笑教會歌<br />\n係得啲兒歌同教會歌先會唔啱音又冇問題<br />\n英文日文韓文，本身就係唔講聲調，冇哩個問題<br />\n但普通話四聲，都冇哩個問題<br />\n我查到泰文同越南文都有分聲調，有冇巴絲知佢地嘅歌又有冇好似廣東歌咁歌詞要啱聲調？<br />\n<br />\n另外廣東歌歌詞又要求啱音韻，又要好有意境，重詞多過曲，係咪都唔太常見於其他地區？"},{"pid":"a2912f67c14d5e6662bd77005295bb0e2f6d4810","tid":1033223,"uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"普通話都要㗎<br />\n國際歌嗰d咪示範唔啱音"},{"pid":"f927c717cc658471e0c1f5974e6620301dc18a6b","tid":1033223,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"想知+1"},{"pid":"3cedc90fa956f37896deb56eccf535a9c5dacbf5","tid":1033223,"uid":186412,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"會唔會係因為廣州話有6個調<br />\n都足夠應付音付高低<br />\n唔啱音會好突兀<br />\n而普通話得4聲<br />\n唔夠用"},{"pid":"38246f81888ec4a0ad7cdfb72d77efea11787258","tid":1033223,"uid":182846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a2bf2de194c2f8ac9055716404a18293bc2629f","tid":1033223,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:23:15.000Z","msg":"日文都要"},{"pid":"8a64a125a23cdbdf078f44166a48678c04114cfd","tid":1033223,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2912f67c14d5e6662bd77005295bb0e2f6d4810","tid":1033223,"uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"普通話都要㗎<br />\n國際歌嗰d咪示範唔啱音"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T07:40:08.000Z","msg":"有咩？聽過都唔跟聲調喎"},{"pid":"f3935d4d724e00c25905d4bf687dd760739024d1","tid":1033223,"uid":33429,"like":0,"d